{
  "chapter": 42,
  "chapter_summary": "第四十三回 了若指掌\n\n谢晓峰在神秘老人的船舱中醒来，老人告知他身体恢复迅速，但提出以命换命的交易：谢晓峰必须在月圆之夜去枫林外杀死一个等在那里的人。老人透露那人也在等着杀他，两人之间有着深仇大恨。谢晓峰别无选择，只能接受。\n\n谢晓峰来到枫林外的小客栈休养。客栈老板是个迟钝臃肿的老人，其妻青青年轻貌美，主动勾引谢晓峰。青青坦白自己是为了钱才这样做，甚至承认丈夫也知情。谢晓峰与她发生了关系。\n\n深夜，真正的来客并非青青，而是慕容秋荻。她伪装成青青接近谢晓峰，坦承自己仍爱着他，所以用这种方式让他接受自己。本章揭示了谢晓峰内心的孤独与宿命感，以及他与燕十三之间不可避免的对决即将到来。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "有种人好像天生就比别人走运些，连老天爷都总是会特别照顾他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你就是这种人，你复原得远比我想像中快得多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "只要再过两三天，你就可以完全复原。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "然后我就要替你去杀那个人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这是我用你的一条命换来的条件。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "所以我一定要去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "一定。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "我杀过人，我并不在乎多杀一个。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "可是这个人我连他的面都没有见过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我会让你见到他的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "只要见到他，你也非杀他不可。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为他该死！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "你真的这么恨他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我恨他，远比任何人想像中都恨得厉害。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为我这一生就是被他害了的，若不是因为他，一定会活得比现在快乐得多。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "今天已经是十三。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "十三？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "月圆的那天晚上，你就会看见他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "他会到这里来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他不会来，可是你会去，你一定要去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "就从这条路去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你一直往前走，就会看见一片枫林，枫林外有家小小的酒店，你不妨到那里住下来，好好的睡两天。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "然后呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "等到十五的那天晚上，圆月升起时，你从那酒店后门外一条小路走入枫林，就会看见我要你去杀的那个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "我怎么认得出他就是那个人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "只要你看见了他，就一定能认得出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为他也是在那里等着杀我的人，你一定可以感觉到那股杀气！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他看见你时，也一定能感觉到你的杀气，所以你就算不出手，他也一样会杀你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "看来我好像已完全没有选择的余地。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你本来就没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "可是你怎么会知道他在那里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我们本就约好了在那里相见的，他不死，我就要死在他手里，这其间也完全没有选择的余地。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这就是我们的命运，谁也没法子逃避。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在你已经可以走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "现在你就要我走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在我就要你走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为我们的交易已经谈成了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "难道我们不能交个朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为有种人天生就不能有朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "你是这种人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不管我是不是这种人都一样，因为你是这种人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "没有人能够改变自己的命运，如果你一定想改变他，结果只有更不幸。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你一定要记住这句话，这是我从无数次惨痛经验中得来的教训。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你也一定要记住，一定要好好的睡两天。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为那个人绝不是容易对付的，你需要恢复体力。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "我还需要什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "还需要一点运气，和一把剑，一把很快的剑！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "下次你到客人房里去的时候，最好穿上件比较厚的衣裳。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你不是个好人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我本来就不是。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你根本不想要我去换件比较厚的衣裳，你只想要我把这身衣裳也脱光。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你心里虽然这么样想，嘴里却不敢说出来，因为我是别人的老婆。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "难道你不是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我是不是别人的老婆都一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "一样……？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我本来就是为了要勾引你来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为你不是好人，长得却不错，因为你看起来不像穷光蛋，我却很需要赚点钱花，我只会用这种法子赚钱，我不勾引你勾引准？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我的丈夫也知道这一点，这地方赚的钱，连他一个人都养不活，他只有让我用这种法子来赚钱，甚至连那两个小伙计的工钱，都是我用这种法子付给他们的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是你。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 403,
      "line_end": 403
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "是我。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 407,
      "line_end": 407
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我知道你本来一定连做梦都想不到会是我的。",
      "tone": "讥讽",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 409,
      "line_end": 409
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我知道你一定很想要个女人，每当你紧张的时候，你都会这样子的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 417,
      "line_end": 417
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "可是我知道你一定不会要我。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 421,
      "line_end": 421
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "除了我之外，什么样的女人都不会拒绝，可是你一定会拒绝我。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 423,
      "line_end": 423
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "所以你才会这么样做！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 425,
      "line_end": 425
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "只有用这种法子，我才能让你要我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 427,
      "line_end": 427
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "你为了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 429,
      "line_end": 429
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "为了我还是喜欢你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 431,
      "line_end": 431
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "你看得出我很紧张？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 443,
      "line_end": 443
    }
